---
// FAQ and Backstory section
import FAQAccordion from './FAQAccordion.tsx';
---

<section class="section-spacing bg-cream">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <!-- Backstory Section -->
    <div id="backstory" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Why I Built This</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70">
          By Cristobal Grana, Lead UX Engineer at GoDaddy
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            I've built design systems from scratch three times now. First at a startup
            where we moved fast and broke things. Then at a scale-up where we had to
            retrofit governance onto existing chaos. Now at an enterprise where
            everything needs process and approval.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Each time, I spent months doing the same things: setting up tokens,
            creating Figma files, configuring build tools, writing documentation,
            establishing contribution guidelines. The pattern was always the same, but
            I couldn't find a good starting point that wasn't either too opinionated
            or too bare-bones.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            So I built Trellis—the starter kit I wish I had when I began. It's not a
            library you import. It's a foundation you own. Customize it, extend it,
            make it yours. Skip the 6 months of infrastructure work and start building
            the things that matter: your products.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed italic text-charcoal/70">
            Design systems shouldn't take half a year to set up. Let's fix that.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div id="faq" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70">
          Everything you need to know about Trellis
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Accordion (React Component) -->
      <FAQAccordion client:only="react" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
